 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Identify
@60017 = ~Wand of Identify~
@60018 = ~This wand will use 1 charge to identify an item, much like a scroll of Identify, in that to identify an item you right-click on that item. A menu will appear and from here you choose the "Scroll" option. The chance of identifying the item is 100%. The charge will identify the item's name, what it does, and if it is cursed.

STATISTICS:
(Divination)

Charge abilities:
– Identify
  – Identify an item by using 1 charge
  Range: Touch
  Duration: Instant
  Area of Effect: 1 item
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Infravision
@60019 = ~Wand of Infravision~
@60020 = ~This wand will grant the ability to see with infravision, just as an elf or dwarf can.

