 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Sleep
@60029 = ~Wand of Sleep~
@60030 = ~This wand will emit a gold beam of energy at its targets up to a maximum range of 60 ft., affecting a 15-ft. radius. If the target creatures fail their Save vs. Death (with -3 penalty), they will fall into a deep, comatose sleep for %duration%. Monsters with 5 Hit Dice or more are unaffected. Attacks against sleeping opponents never miss.

