//Chill Touch
@60031 = ~Wand of Chill Touch~
@60032 = ~When activated, a blue glow encompasses the wielder's hand, and <PRO_HESHE> uses this energy to attack the life force of an adjacent creature. The creature is punched for 1d2 fist damage (Strength bonuses apply) and must make a Saving Throw vs. Wand or suffer 1d8 points of cold damage and receive a -2 THAC0 penalty for 5 rounds. Nonliving creatures such as golems and undead are unaffected by this spell.

