//Bless
@60100 = ~Wand of Bless~
@60101 = ~With activation, this wand releases the power of a prayerful blessing, raising the morale of friendly creatures by +1. Furthermore, it raises their attack and damage rolls by +1. The wielder determines a point (up to 40 ft. away) where the effect will occur, affecting all creatures in a 15-ft. radius centered on the point selected by the wielder (thus, affected creatures leaving the area are still subject to the effects; those entering the area after are not).

STATISTICS:
(Conjuration/Summoning)

Charge abilities:
– Bless
  – Morale +1
  – Attack rolls +1
  – Damage rolls +1
  Range: 40 ft.
  Duration: 6 rounds
  Area of Effect: 15-ft. radius
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Command
@60102 = ~Wand of Command~
@60103 = ~This wand enables the wielder to command another creature to sleep for a single round. At the end of the round, the creature awakens and is unharmed. Creatures with 6 or more Hit Dice are entitled to a Saving Throw vs. Wand to ignore the command.

