//Sanctuary
@60114 = ~Wand of Sanctuary~
@60115 = ~This wand causes all of the wielder's opponents to ignore <PRO_HISHER> existence as if <PRO_HESHE> were invisible. While protected by this spell, the subject cannot take direct offensive action without breaking the spell, but may use non-attack spells or otherwise act in any way that does not violate the prohibition against offensive action. This allows a warded person to heal wounds, for example, or to Bless <PRO_HIMHER>self. The wielder cannot cast spells on other creatures without ending the spell.

STATISTICS:
(Abjuration)

Charge abilities:
– Sanctuary
  – Ignored as if invisible
  – Can move, use thief skills, and heal/buff self
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: Self
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Shillelagh
@60116 = ~Wand of Shillelagh~
@60117 = ~When activated, this wand creates a magical cudgel that has a +1 bonus to its attack roll and inflicts 2d4 points of damage on opponents.

STATISTICS:
(Alteration)

Charge abilities:
– Shillelagh
  – Creates weightless magical club
    – Deals 2d4 crushing damage
    – +1 bonus to THAC0
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: Self
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Armor of Faith
@60118 = ~Wand of Armor of Faith~
@60119 = ~When activated, the wielder receives significant protection against melee, ranged, and magical attacks. This magical armor is a force of energy that absorbs %magnitude%% of the damage intended for the wielder.

STATISTICS:
(Abjuration)

Charge abilities:
– Armor of Faith
  – Absorbs %magnitude%% of incoming damage
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: Self
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Doom
@60120 = ~Wand of Doom~
@60121 = ~When activated, this wand causes a feeling of doom to overwhelm the target. For the duration of the spell, the target receives a -2 penalty to <PRO_HISHER> THAC0 and Saving Throws. There is no Saving Throw for this spell.

STATISTICS:
(Alteration)

Charge abilities:
– Doom
  – -2 penalty to THAC0
  – -2 penalty to saving throws
  Range: 25 ft.
  Duration: 1 turn
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~
